{"tid":496527,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Instagram Direct 宣佈獨立！變成單獨一個通訊 App","createTime":"2017-12-11T18:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T01:53:37.000Z","uid":10958,"like":3,"dislike":391,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"68e4f5dd3071227da9292b90336e30130e3875dc","tid":496527,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:25:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>Instagram Direct 宣佈獨立！變成單獨一個通訊 App</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mQQsKzOnyzh91YEaD3z6Yg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjcwO2g9MzUxO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/052d2ee7a498054c45a47cd31d740ee3/tumblr_inline_p0ob04T7PM1us2n2v_1280.png.cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmQQsKzOnyzh91YEaD3z6Yg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjcwO2g9MzUxO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F052d2ee7a498054c45a47cd31d740ee3%2Ftumblr_inline_p0ob04T7PM1us2n2v_1280.png.cf.jpg&h=5733a927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋玩 Instagram 時，見到別人的 Story 幾得意有趣，就會 Inbox 講一句「正！」「WOW！」「So Cute！」，但將來 IG 用家想發訊息予另一個 IG 用家，就可能要另外打開一個 App。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DiXHc9vDGTc1m.VUUzp2JA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NTI5O2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/a70f66fafb4afd546ab963a5c568a836/tumblr_inline_p0ob05JmZu1us2n2v_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDiXHc9vDGTc1m.VUUzp2JA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NTI5O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2Fa70f66fafb4afd546ab963a5c568a836%2Ftumblr_inline_p0ob05JmZu1us2n2v_1280.jpg&h=c7b3275a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n實際上 Instagram 本身內置的訊息功能名為 &ldquo;Direct&quot;，但 &quot;Direct&rdquo; 來年可能會由一個功能，變成一個獨立的 App，Instagram 這個「分拆上市」的動作已經在 6 個國家：智利、以色列、意大利、葡萄牙、土耳其及烏拉圭 進行當中，用家在 App Store 下載 &ldquo;Direct&rdquo; 之後，Instagram 本身的 Inbox 就會消失。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eDwqvZcPSoEIu8V9bxwjtw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://78.media.tumblr.com/992c6d635af3868f74ad2dc789479ce6/tumblr_inline_p0ob06hFs31us2n2v_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FeDwqvZcPSoEIu8V9bxwjtw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F992c6d635af3868f74ad2dc789479ce6%2Ftumblr_inline_p0ob06hFs31us2n2v_1280.jpg&h=efb3db7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n產品主管 Hemal Shah 表示，此舉是希望將「公開」與「私人」的功能分開，當用家想公開地發佈靚相時，就可用 Instagram；想與個別朋友分享秘密時就可用 Direct。大家又認為此舉是善舉？還是多此一舉？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/instagram-direct-%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-%E8%AE%8A%E6%88%90%E5%96%AE%E7%8D%A8-%E5%80%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A-1834716772917302.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkstylemen.yahoo.com%2Finstagram-direct-%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E5%2580%258B%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A8%258A-1834716772917302.html&d=tuGvIcROGMhMWQwFqHGIOGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=d00e5443\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/instagram-direct-%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-%E8%AE%8A%E6%88%90%E5%96%AE%E7%8D%A8-%E5%80%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A-1834716772917302.html</a>"},{"pid":"788201117cf433e21cc116f45470cfc5c76a5b3b","tid":496527,"uid":31602,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"Snapchat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507a5286e3ff2da079b41e89a9c27a1afb6cc10b","tid":496527,"uid":5843,"like":263,"dislike":6,"score":257,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:27:36.000Z","msg":"好似fb同messenger咁拆app<br />\n又逼你down多啲野on99"},{"pid":"a91428f9db8771530f2832888d5c8be4efb8d1eb","tid":496527,"uid":15345,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似fb同me